file.name: two-responses.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Test
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://test/'
paths:
  /test:
    get:
      summary: Test
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  test:
                    type: string
        '422':
          description: Validation failed
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  test:
                    type: string
